high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the coffee machine on the counter.
Take the mug out of the coffee machine.
Walk over to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the mug inside. Close the refrigerator. Wait a few seconds. Open the refrigerator. Take the mug out. Close the refrigerator.
Walk back over to the coffee machine.
Place the mug inside the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug inside the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left and face the coffee maker.
Pick up the coffee mug.
Walk right and face the fridge.
Put the mug on the bottom right shelf of the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, and take it out.
Take a step left and face the coffee maker again.
Put the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around then face right to face the coffee machine.
Grab the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn right and face the fridge on the left.
Chill the mug in the fridge for 5 seconds.
Turn left and head back to the coffee machine.
Place the mug back in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled mug in the coffee machine.

high_descs: turn left, walk to the coffee machine on the right
grab the cup in the coffee machine
turn right, walk to the refrigerator
put the cup in the refrigerator, wait a while, take the cup out
turn left, walk to the coffee machine
put the cup in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: cool the cup in the refrigerator, put the cup back in the coffee machine

high_descs: Turn around, go to the coffee machine on the right.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the fridge on the right.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Bring the chilled mug back to the coffee machine on the left.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the coffee maker, and face the coffee maker.
Take the cup from the coffee maker.
Turn right, walk towards the fridge, and face the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the cup in front of the bread, close the fridge, wait for it to cool down, and take the cup out of the fridge.
Turn left and walk towards the coffee maker and face the coffee maker.
Place the cup back on the coffee maker.
